2015
Serpent Encryption Software – WPF app showcasing the use of advanced modern cryptography
features Serpent algorithm written from scratch in C# (at the time there was no functional implementation in that language that I was aware of)
allows encrypting and decrypting files of any size using password or raw key
includes ECB and CBC Block Cipher Modes as well as both Standard and BitSlice (optimised) versions of Serpent Cipher
works asynchronously, gives rich feedback, supports any valid key, allows randomization of keys and passwords, allows dragging and dropping files
shows legacy techniques and allows to see how the thought process used in modern programming as well as my knowledge have both evolved over the years (these is one of my earliest projects)
